				\begin{document}$$_3$$\end{document} is basically due to the conversion of respiratory pigments into forms that are incapable of transporting and releasing oxygen, which means nitrate must previously be converted to nitrite under the internal conditions of the animal?\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
